imgui.cubecode.windows.events.title: Events
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.server_sta: This event is triggered when the server loads. (not worlds)
This event is triggered when the server is loaded.
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.server_tic: This event is triggered when the server starts ticking (i.e. §720§r times per second)
This event is triggered when the server finishes ticking (i.e. §720§r times per second)
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.block_play: Block: before break by a player
This cancelable event is triggered before the player destroys a block in the world.

&6blockPos&r - Block position. 
&6blockState&r - ScriptBlockState of block. 
&6blockEntity&r - ScriptBlockEntity of block
Block: after break by a player
This event is triggered after the player destroys a block in the world.

&6blockPos&r - Block position. 
&6blockState&r - ScriptBlockState of block. 
&6blockEntity&r - ScriptBlockEntity of block
Block: canceled break by a player
This event is triggered after canceling any block destruction event by a player in the world.

&6blockPos&r - Block position. 
&6blockState&r - ScriptBlockState of block. 
&6blockEntity&r - ScriptBlockEntity of block
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.player_dea:
This cancelable event is triggered when the player dies.

The simple tip: if you want to cancel death, make sure to give the player some health, otherwise he will fall into a perpetual dying cycle.
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.player_res: This event is triggered when the player is respawns.

&6oldPlayer&r - Player before respawn. 
&6alive&r - If the player is alive
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.player_att: This cancelable event is triggered when a player attacks a block.
This cancelable event is triggered when the player attacks an entity.
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.player_int: This cancelable event is triggered when the player interacts with a block.

&6blockPos&r - Block position. 
&6hand&r - Name hand. 
&6direction&r - Direction. 
&6isInsideBlock&r, Is inside block.
This cancelable event is triggered when the player interacts with an entity.
This cancelable event is triggered when the player interacts with an item.
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.entity_hur: This cancelable event gets triggered when a mob/a player gets hurt (damaged).
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.entity_bef: This cancelable event is triggered before the death of the mob/player.
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.entity_aft: This event is triggered after the death of the mob/player.
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.entity_kil: This event is triggered when an entity is killed by another entity.
imgui.cubecode.windows.events.world_tick: This event is triggered when the world starts ticking.
This event comes when the world finishes ticking.
imgui.cubecode.windows.settings.appearan: After adding the font to the config, reload the game.
